{"article_id":"tnmO9rKyVqdqHnms","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"( CNN )","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"More than 20,000 people have died from the coronavirus in the United States ,","depth":9},{"id":2,"text":"which now has more reported deaths than any country in the world ,","depth":9},{"id":3,"text":"according to a tally from Johns Hopkins University .","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"The US death toll on Saturday climbed to 20,389 ,","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"surpassing that of Italy ,","depth":10},{"id":6,"text":"which is reporting 19,468 deaths ,","depth":10},{"id":7,"text":"per Johns Hopkins .","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"At least 2,074 deaths were reported in the US on Friday , the largest increase in coronavirus fatalities","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"the country has seen since the beginning of the outbreak .","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"At least 524,903people have tested positive for the virus ,","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"according to Johns Hopkins .","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"Of the deaths reported Friday , 783 occurred in New York state ,","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"bringing the statewide death toll to 8,627 ,","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"Gov . Andrew Cuomo said Saturday .","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"That was a slight drop from the state 's all-time high in single-day fatalities ,","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"which occurred Wednesday with 799 deaths .","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"There were 777 deaths Thursday .","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"`` You can see","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"that the number is somewhat stabilizing ,","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"but it is stabilizing at a horrific rate , ''","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"Cuomo said .","depth":7},{"id":22,"text":"`` These are just incredible numbers","depth":7},{"id":23,"text":"depicting incredible loss and pain . ''","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"But Cuomo also shared what he called good news ,","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"saying","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"the state 's curve `` is continuing to flatten . ''","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"`` The number of hospitalizations appears to have hit an apex ,","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"and the apex appears to be a plateau , ''","depth":10},{"id":29,"text":"the governor said ,","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"where numbers will level out for a period","depth":10},{"id":31,"text":"before dropping .","depth":10},{"id":32,"text":"The hospitalization rate is also down ,","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"Cuomo said ,","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"as are the number of intensive-care admissions .","depth":8},{"id":35,"text":"`` Still people getting infected , ''","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"he said ,","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"`` still people going into the hospital ,","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"but again , a lower rate of increase . ''","depth":8},{"id":39,"text":"The US likely saw a peak in its daily death toll ,","depth":7},{"id":40,"text":"according to Dr. Chris Murray , the director of the Institute for Health Metrics and Evaluation at the University of Washington","depth":8},{"id":41,"text":"--","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"who created the model","depth":10},{"id":43,"text":"the White House is using","depth":11},{"id":44,"text":"to gauge the peak of coronavirus cases .","depth":11},{"id":45,"text":"`` We re-run the model , basically , almost every night","depth":8},{"id":46,"text":"-- and the new returns from different states are suggesting different peaks in different states ,","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"but at the national level we seem to be pretty much close to the peak , ''","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"he said Friday .","depth":7},{"id":49,"text":"That model projects","depth":7},{"id":50,"text":"about 61,500 Americans will lose their lives to the virus by August","depth":8},{"id":51,"text":"-- if the country keeps social distance measures in place until the end of May .","depth":8},{"id":52,"text":"If they factor in states","depth":9},{"id":53,"text":"that may lift these rules by May 1 ,","depth":9},{"id":54,"text":"the numbers `` do n't look good , ''","depth":8},{"id":55,"text":"Murray said .","depth":7},{"id":56,"text":"While health experts are encouraged by signs","depth":7},{"id":57,"text":"that social distancing measures are having a positive impact ,","depth":7},{"id":58,"text":"they warn","depth":7},{"id":59,"text":"re-opening the country too quickly could set the US back .","depth":7},{"id":60,"text":"Despite the positive signs ,","depth":8},{"id":61,"text":"the US had not yet reached its peak in cases ,","depth":8},{"id":62,"text":"Dr. Deborah Birx , the White House coronavirus coordinator , said Friday .","depth":7},{"id":63,"text":"`` So every day we need to continue to do what we did yesterday , and the week before , and the week before that ,","depth":8},{"id":64,"text":"because that 's what in the end is going to take us up across the peak and down the other side , ''","depth":8},{"id":65,"text":"she said .","depth":7},{"id":66,"text":"Saturday marked the first time","depth":6},{"id":67,"text":"every US state was under a federal disaster declaration simultaneously ,","depth":6},{"id":68,"text":"after President Donald Trump approved one such declaration for Wyoming .","depth":5},{"id":69,"text":"It was the 55th disaster declaration","depth":6},{"id":70,"text":"issued in response to the coronavirus ,","depth":6},{"id":71,"text":"following others in the other 49 states , the District of Columbia , the US Virgin Islands , the Northern Mariana Islands , Guam and Puerto Rico .","depth":5},{"id":72,"text":"New York City mayor , governor in dispute over school closures","depth":5},{"id":73,"text":"In New York City , Mayor Bill de Blasio announced Saturday","depth":8},{"id":74,"text":"that schools there would remain closed through the end of the school year","depth":9},{"id":75,"text":"while students continued to receive remote instruction .","depth":9},{"id":76,"text":"the mayor 's `` opinion . ''","depth":7},{"id":77,"text":"But that was soon undercut by Gov . Cuomo ,","depth":7},{"id":78,"text":"who said","depth":11},{"id":79,"text":"that `` no decision '' had been made on closing schools through the end of the year ,","depth":11},{"id":80,"text":"adding","depth":11},{"id":81,"text":"he valuedthe mayor 's `` opinion . ''","depth":11},{"id":82,"text":"`` We may do that ,","depth":12},{"id":83,"text":"but we 're going to do it in a coordinated sense with the other localities , ''","depth":12},{"id":84,"text":"Cuomo said ,","depth":11},{"id":85,"text":"adding :","depth":11},{"id":86,"text":"`` It makes no sense for one locality to take an action","depth":12},{"id":87,"text":"that 's not coordinated with the others . ''","depth":12},{"id":88,"text":"De Blasio said Saturday evening","depth":10},{"id":89,"text":"he and the governor would always `` work things through in the common interest of our people . ''","depth":10},{"id":90,"text":"`` But the bottom line is my responsibility is not to the federal government , the state government ,","depth":12},{"id":91,"text":"my responsibility is not to another elected official .","depth":12},{"id":92,"text":"My responsibility is to those kids , those parents , those educators","depth":12},{"id":93,"text":"who need to be safe , ''","depth":12},{"id":94,"text":"de Blasio said .","depth":10},{"id":95,"text":"Additionally , Cuomo said","depth":8},{"id":96,"text":"no decision has been made on when businesses will reopen .","depth":8},{"id":97,"text":"That step ,","depth":9},{"id":98,"text":"he said ,","depth":9},{"id":99,"text":"should be coordinated with schools .","depth":8},{"id":100,"text":"The state will gather the best minds","depth":9},{"id":101,"text":"to study","depth":10},{"id":102,"text":"whether reopening the economy would trigger a `` second wave '' of infections ,","depth":10},{"id":103,"text":"Cuomo said .","depth":8},{"id":104,"text":"`` The worst thing","depth":11},{"id":105,"text":"that can happen","depth":11},{"id":106,"text":"is we make a misstep","depth":10},{"id":107,"text":"and we let our emotions get ahead of our logic and fact ,","depth":10},{"id":108,"text":"and we go through this again in any manner , shape or form , ''","depth":10},{"id":109,"text":"he said .","depth":8},{"id":110,"text":"President Trump ,","depth":10},{"id":111,"text":"who two weeks ago said","depth":11},{"id":112,"text":"he wanted the country to open by Easter ,","depth":11},{"id":113,"text":"said Friday","depth":10},{"id":114,"text":"he would n't do anything","depth":11},{"id":115,"text":"until he knew","depth":12},{"id":116,"text":"the country was healthy again .","depth":12},{"id":117,"text":"But internally , officials are pushing to reopen the country by next month ,","depth":11},{"id":118,"text":"with specific discussions underway about May 1 ,","depth":11},{"id":119,"text":"a person familiar with the talks told CNN","depth":10},{"id":120,"text":"`` I 'm going to have to make a decision","depth":12},{"id":121,"text":"and I only hope to God","depth":13},{"id":122,"text":"that it 's right decision , ''","depth":13},{"id":123,"text":"the President said Friday .","depth":11},{"id":124,"text":"`` But I would say","depth":12},{"id":125,"text":"without question","depth":12},{"id":126,"text":"it 's the biggest decision","depth":12},{"id":127,"text":"I 've ever had to make . ''","depth":12},{"id":128,"text":"In Ohio , the number of people","depth":10},{"id":129,"text":"impacted","depth":10},{"id":130,"text":"is lower","depth":10},{"id":131,"text":"than previously projected .","depth":10},{"id":132,"text":"But","depth":11},{"id":133,"text":"before the state attempts a return to normal life ,","depth":11},{"id":134,"text":"Gov . Mike DeWine said","depth":11},{"id":135,"text":"more work needs to be done","depth":12},{"id":136,"text":"and there will need to be `` a lot more testing . ''","depth":12},{"id":137,"text":"`` The reopening is going to have to be ,","depth":12},{"id":138,"text":"you know ,","depth":13},{"id":139,"text":"one step at a time , one stage at a time , ''","depth":13},{"id":140,"text":"he said ,","depth":11},{"id":141,"text":"adding ,","depth":11},{"id":142,"text":"`` We do n't want to be premature ,","depth":12},{"id":143,"text":"but we also want to assure people","depth":13},{"id":144,"text":"that we 're planning for this . ''","depth":13},{"id":145,"text":"Meanwhile , local and state officials are cracking down on mass gatherings like church services","depth":10},{"id":146,"text":"as Easter weekend begins .","depth":10},{"id":147,"text":"In Kentucky , authorities will record license plates of those","depth":13},{"id":148,"text":"who show up to any gatherings","depth":13},{"id":149,"text":"and hand that information over to the local health department ,","depth":13},{"id":150,"text":"which will require those individuals to stay quarantined for 14 days ,","depth":13},{"id":151,"text":"Gov . Andy Beshear announced .","depth":11},{"id":152,"text":"The state is down to less than seven churches statewide","depth":13},{"id":153,"text":"that are still `` thinking about '' having an in-person service this weekend ,","depth":13},{"id":154,"text":"he said .","depth":12},{"id":155,"text":"In a news conference Saturday , Beshear recognized","depth":13},{"id":156,"text":"that it would be hard on people to not be `` in our houses of worship , or with our families , or doing Easter egg hunts with a bunch of kids . ''","depth":13},{"id":157,"text":"`` But know , ''","depth":14},{"id":158,"text":"he said ,","depth":14},{"id":159,"text":"`` that the sacrifice is worth it . ''","depth":13},{"id":160,"text":"In New Mexico , Gov . Michelle Lujan Grisham said","depth":10},{"id":161,"text":"the state amended a public health order","depth":11},{"id":162,"text":"banning mass gatherings","depth":12},{"id":163,"text":"to include houses of worship .","depth":12},{"id":164,"text":"In a tweet , the governor wrote ,","depth":10},{"id":165,"text":"`` The risk is simply too great .","depth":11},{"id":166,"text":"In-person services risk spreading # COVID19","depth":12},{"id":167,"text":"potentially affecting thousands . ''","depth":12},{"id":168,"text":"Multiple state leaders said","depth":11},{"id":169,"text":"social distancing measures are having an effect .","depth":11},{"id":170,"text":"Hospitalizations in Connecticut are dropping .","depth":11},{"id":171,"text":"Arkansas also saw the lowest number of hospitalizations","depth":14},{"id":172,"text":"compared to neighboring states .","depth":14},{"id":173,"text":"The number of affected people in Ohio is lower than previously projected .","depth":13},{"id":174,"text":"And in California , hospitals saw a nearly 2 % drop in ICU patients .","depth":13},{"id":175,"text":"In New Jersey cases climbed to 58,151 ,","depth":15},{"id":176,"text":"Gov . Phil Murphy said Saturday .","depth":15},{"id":177,"text":"But","depth":16},{"id":178,"text":"while that number is `` scary , ''","depth":17},{"id":179,"text":"the state is `` beginning to beat this virus back , ''","depth":17},{"id":180,"text":"he said .","depth":15},{"id":181,"text":"Government projections","depth":14},{"id":182,"text":"obtained by The New York Times","depth":14},{"id":183,"text":"show","depth":13},{"id":184,"text":"coronavirus infections and deaths could dramatically increase","depth":13},{"id":185,"text":"if social distancing and other measures were lifted after 30 days .","depth":13},{"id":186,"text":"If stay-at-home orders were lifted after a month ,","depth":13},{"id":187,"text":"the government report says ,","depth":13},{"id":188,"text":"there would be a bump in the demand for ventilators","depth":14},{"id":189,"text":"and the US death toll could reach 200,000 ,","depth":14},{"id":190,"text":"the Times reported .","depth":13},{"id":191,"text":"A Health and Human Services spokesperson told CNN ,","depth":12},{"id":192,"text":"`` We do not comment on any alleged , leaked documents . ''","depth":12},{"id":193,"text":"CNN has reached out to the Department of Homeland Security for comment .","depth":11},{"id":194,"text":"Murray told CNN Friday night","depth":10},{"id":195,"text":"that","depth":11},{"id":196,"text":"if mitigation measures were lifted by May 1 ,","depth":12},{"id":197,"text":"cases could go back up in the summer .","depth":12},{"id":198,"text":"`` If we were to stop at the national level May 1st ,","depth":12},{"id":199,"text":"we 're seeing","depth":15},{"id":200,"text":"( in models )","depth":15},{"id":201,"text":"a return to almost where we are now sometime in July ,","depth":14},{"id":202,"text":"so a rebound . ''","depth":13},{"id":203,"text":"Murray said .","depth":11},{"id":204,"text":"`` There 's a very substantial risk of rebound","depth":11},{"id":205,"text":"if we do n't wait to the point","depth":12},{"id":206,"text":"where most transmission is near zero in each state . ''","depth":12}],"relations":[{"parent":413,"left":0,"right":412,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":412,"left":271,"right":411,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":271,"left":244,"right":270,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":244,"left":223,"right":243,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":223,"left":217,"right":222,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":217,"left":213,"right":216,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":213,"left":209,"right":212,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":209,"left":208,"right":3,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":208,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":212,"left":4,"right":211,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":211,"left":210,"right":7,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":210,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":216,"left":214,"right":215,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":214,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":215,"left":10,"right":11,"relation":"attribution","nucleari